reviewText: It was very entertaining and put you in the Christmas Spirit. He drew you in to the DVD. I had my sister come over and had her watch it, so she went home and purchased it..I diffinetly will recommend this to  frineds.and family. B E Taylor seems that he really loves what he is doing and cares about people.
"Where I Find You" is great for worship and love to the Lord.  Sometimes I dance, and I'm 71 years old.
